title: Beware the Creeper (01 - 05) (2003) (digital) (Tithe-Empire)
description:
Beware the Creeper (01 - 05) (2003) (digital) (Tithe-Empire)


Get ready for a unique VERTIGO twist on one of DC's strangest characters. In this new 5- issue miniseries by Jason Hall (Pistolwhip) and Cliff Chiang (BATMAN: THE GOLDEN STREETS OF GOTHAM), a bizarre, colorful creature of the night stalks the streets of 1920s Paris: The Creeper. The enigmatic hero has her sights set on the upper class, but what are the true motivations behind The Creeper's actions?
